title: Santa Cruz - Cruzin’ Puerto Rico
description:
"We are proud to present our full length edit of SC CRUZIN' in Puerto Rico 🇵🇷 Hop in the van with Fabiana Delfino, Maurio McCoy, Jake Wooten, Jereme Knibbs, Kevin Braun & Erick Winkowski as they shred all the island life has to offer. You've seen the vlogs, now see the clips! Special thanks to Sota, Emil, The Guava House & everyone who made us feel at home, we hope to be back soon!" -Santa Cruz Skateboards. 

Additional filming: Harry Bergenfield, Fabiana Delfino, Erick Winkowski.
